76561198020144608,Recommended,256290,20370170,"Posted: 7 January, 2016",all,Clark Kent,"If the game won't play for you [you press play, but nothing loads, even though Steam says you are in game]1) Open Uplay (make sure Uplay is updated and current) while Steam is not running.2) Open Steam3) Attempt to run 'Child of Light' in Steam. A pop-up with a serial key will appear. Copy this number, but do not press 'Play' or 'Run Game' or whatever.4) Find an icon in Uplay (I think in 'Games' tab). It will say Activate Game or something. Click on this, and enter the serial key from (3) above. The game should now be activated.5) Go back to Steam, and run the game.Hope it works for you."
