l presented, you will have no problem telling what buff/debuff you have at any given time, but how long do they have left? well, I couldnt really tell until they fall-off along with the visual ques.according to the Uplay unlocks, I have completed all but 2 side quests in the game, the side quests are usually fairly straight forward, you will end up picking them up along the main story and doesnt take muccch time to do, I mostly stumbled onto them while trying to reaching the next zone. or got lost in a maze and ended up in the side quest objective.overall 9/10 game.P.S i love the artstyle and Coeur de Pirate's wonderful music,"
