,Recommended,256290,31038458,Posted: 9 April,all,TinTans,"Great game, beautiful.  Loved the dialog and the story.You come across various characters with different abilities and you get to choose how to upgrade them.  You can also install various crystals for upgrades and the crystals themselves can be combined to make even better crystals!The battle mechanics are totally unique.  There's a timeline of sorts so you can see how soon each character's turn is coming up. You can cause certain enemies to slow down on the timeline or get pushed back either with abilities, the light or by interrupting them (hitting them when they're almost about to have their turn).  Using this to your advantage made the fights really interesting and fun.One thing that wasn't great was that the ending felt rushed for some reason.  I remember thinking I'd have a chance to look over my upgrades and crystals one last time but then suddenly I was whisked into the final battle when I wasn't expecting it!"
